            $$n_{n0} = N_D = n_i$$
            $$J_p = q \mu_p p_n(x_n) E(x_n) - q D_p \frac{d\Delta p_n(x)}{dx}$$
            $$J_n = q \mu_n n_n(x_n) E(x_n) + q D_n \frac{d\Delta n_n(x)}{dx}$$
